Creating and sending a transaction TX and evaluating dynamic update of variables  
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Define TxValue = lognormal(MeanNormalTxValue,SigmaNormalTxValue,MinTxValue)
TotalRiskTxValue = calculate TotalRiskValue of TxValue

Define effectiveUsedFactor as the result of the trust-value-time-increase mechanism
Do transaction-creation-parameters-increase using effectiveUsedFactor

Defiine kycVerifierToGo = select KYC Verifier at random
send message to kycVerifierToGo (self, kycVerifierToGo)
NumberOfSentTransactions++




